location.fullValue: Wexner - C Plan, The Shire at Arcadia

data.description: Welcome home to 844 Yorkshire Drive! Located in the Shire at Arcadia in the heart of Alexandria, this property has been meticulously maintained and offers something for everyone! The 2 bedroom 2 bathroom home features a bonus room which can easily be a study, play room, home gym, and more!  An open, spacious layout in the main living spaces provides plenty of room for entertaining while still maintaining privacy from the neighbors. The ensuite primary bathroom boasts a double vanity and separate commode room, and the entire home features many elegant wooden and wainscoting features. The gorgeous view from the back balcony overlooks the woods and offers a retreat from the business of the day, and your own private garage provides welcome convenience. This home is only five years old and is in excellent condition. The community features a large, gorgeous clubhouse and relaxing private pool. Don't miss out! Book your private showing today!
